data.name: Label4.Text
data.value: The Sunset Cove Villa is a spacious and inviting accommodation option at our resort, perfect for daytime gatherings of up to 10 guests. Nestled near the shoreline, this villa hut offers stunning views of the ocean and the surrounding natural beauty. With ample space for relaxation and socializing, including comfortable seating areas and a shaded terrace, guests can enjoy the tranquil ambiance and refreshing sea breeze.
